data.name: StarClass
data.comment: Top right info showing class of star we're jumping towards

data.name: DiscoveredBy
data.comment: Who discovered the star system and when. {0} string, name of a cmdr {1} date, short format

data.name: LastUpdated
data.comment: Appended to DiscoveredBy, shows date system data was last updated {0} date, short format

data.name: TrafficInfo
data.comment: Traffic info from EDSM. {0}, int, count of cmdr's visiting in past 24 hours {1}, int, count of cmdr's visiting in past week {2}, int, count of cmdr's visiting ever

data.name: JumpCounts
data.comment: Shown right of lines of jumps. {0} how many jumps already completed on this journey. {1} total count of jumps in this journey.

data.name: JumpDistance
data.comment: Total distance of this journey in Light Years. {0} float, 1 decimal place

data.name: GuardianBeacon
data.comment: Part of a special line shown when the next system has a Guardian Beacon

data.name: GuardianRuins
data.comment: Part of a special line shown when the next system has guardian Ruins {0} int, how many Ruins are in the system

data.name: GuardianStructures
data.comment: Part of a special line shown when the next system has guardian Structures {0} int, how many Structures are in the system

data.name: SpecialGuardian
data.comment: A line header when the next system has some Guardian sites

data.name: SpecialHopInfo
data.comment: Part of a special line shown when the next system is part of a route we are following {0} int, the index of the next system in the route {1} int, total count of route hops

data.name: SpecialJoiner
data.comment: The character used to join parts of special lines

data.name: SpecialNowEntering
data.comment: A line header when the next system is in a different galactic region

data.name: SpecialRouteHop
data.comment: A line header when the next system is a hop on the route we are following
